plot: Chloe meets Poof for the first time when he comes home from school on Spring Break. Cosmo and Wanda win a free French Dinner, so Chloe gets to babysit Poof and his friends. Everything goes well until Vicky shows up.

When Poof comes home for spring break, Cosmo and Wanda win a free lovely dinner at a French cusine restaurant, but little do they know that Foop tricked then into going into a black hole! So, while they're away, Chloe babysits Poof, Foop, Sammy, and Timmy's Dad, but Vicky thinks there's only room for one babysitter in town!—dejondiaz
